author: @ipsitmalviya7222
text: we may use the the below query to find Nth highest salary.  with salary_cte as (select  salary, dense_rank() over(order by salary desc) as N from employee) select  salary  from salary_cte where N=6;  one may change the value of N to get the salary as required

author: @pradnyaraibagkar250
text: Assignment Solution  9. Write a sql query to determine the 6th highest salary without using limit (N = 6) select salary from employee e1 where N-1 =  (select count(salary) from employee e2 where e2.salary > e1.salary)  select salary from employee e1 where 6-1 = (select count(salary) from employee e2 where e2.salary > e1.salary);
